                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="5 Stars for this excellent movies. &#10;Tomb Raider was the most popular game series of 90's and early 2000, and every kid of those years could tell you that Lara Croft is the 'Biggest Star' of the gaming world. This movie has done justice to Tomb Raider games since the earlier 2 movies were a let down.&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

